      "date": "2016-09-08 15:00:53.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\nI'm seeing the following error with this patch:\n\n[771343.391364] LustreError: 138538:0:(libcfs_string.c:466:cfs_expr_list_values()) Number of values 4 exceeds max allowed 16\n[771343.391507] LNetError: 138538:0:(config.c:172:lnet_ni_alloc()) Failed to set CPTs for NI o2ib1: -22",
