      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified+1\n\nTests uploaded by Trevis Autotest2 from trevis-33vm1 for review-dne-part-1 received by maloo, run on CentOS Linux 7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/fccdf8bc-75f4-11e6-b08e-5254006e85c2). Ran 7 tests. No failures.",
